# Datto RMM OpenAPI codegen (Phase 2)
# spec/openapi.json + spec/openapi-prev.json are committed (they are the reproducibility
# baseline). spec/openapi.patched.json is a transient intermediate produced by
# scripts/patch-spec.mjs on every `npm run generate` run and is never committed.
spec/openapi.patched.json
# The Orval endpoints layer is a transient by-product of the axios target (Orval cannot
# emit types without also emitting endpoint stubs for a spec that declares paths); the
# client never imports it, so it is git-ignored rather than committed.
src/generated/endpoints/
# NOTE: src/generated/types/ and src/generated/schemas/ are intentionally NOT ignored —
# they are committed because they derive from an external spec (finalized in Phase 2).
